    h = 0
    Hmax = 0
    t = 0
    V = Vi
    while t <= T:

        air_density = 1.225 * math.exp(-h / 8500)
        g_at_altitude = g * (1 - 2 * h / (R + h))

        a = (g_at_altitude - k * abs(V) * V / m - drag_force / m) / (1 + h * g_at_altitude / (R * T))
        V += a * dt
        if V <= 0:
            break
        t += dt
        if h > Hmax:
            Hmax = h
    return Hmax
